Package: Trex
Title: Methods for TCR single-cell embedding 
Version: 0.99.3
Date: 2021-11-11
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Nick", family = "Borcherding", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "ncborch@gmail.com"),
    person(given = "Drew", family = "Voigt", role = c("aut"), email = "drewvoigt@gmail.com"))
Description: Implementation of the Trex algorithm for single-cell embedding based on TCR sequences. The package includes a standalone function to calculate multilayered networks from a variety of TCR metrics and interaction with SingleCellExperiment or Seurat data objects. 
